content:
I'm getting this error a lot today. Any idea what it means? The latest time I got it, I was just constraining the US Core Patient profile to add the Must Support flag a couple of places.

All element definitions must have unique ids (diff) ( (ids: Patient,Patient.gender,Patient.birthDate,Patient.deceased[x],Patient.address,Patient.multipleBirth[x],Patient.address.use,Patient.address.use,Patient.address.type)) [differential.element.all(id) and differential.element.id.trace('ids').isDistinct()]
